## Step 6
$P(Z \geq 0.5) = 1 - P(Z < 0.5)$. From the standard normal distribution table, $P(Z < 0.5) \approx 0.6915$. Therefore, $P(Z \geq 0.5) = 1 - 0.6915 = 0.3085$.

